HEADWORD: Predate
<hw>Pre*date"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To date
anticipation; to affix to (a document) an earlier than the actual date;
to antedate; <as>as, a <ex>predated</ex> deed or letter</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

